- The content to be replaced (the anchor text).
- The content that should replace the anchor text.
- The reason for the edit. Keep this reason concise, ideally one word or a short phrase.
- A detailed explanation of the edit.
Your response should be in the following JSON format:
{
  "edits": [
    {
      "contentAnchorText": "The text in the document that this suggested edit is anchored to",
      "suggestedUpdatedContent": "The content that should replace the anchor text",
      "reason": "The reason for the edit",
      "explanation": "A detailed explanation of the edit"
